Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# Gmail Account
IMAPAccount Gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User baserdem.batuhan@gmail.com
PassCmd "$XDG_CONFIG_HOME/mbsync/password.sh"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore Gmail-remote
Account Gmail

MaildirStore Gmail-local
Path ~/Documents/Mail/Gmail/
Inbox ~/Documents/Mail/Gmail/Inbox/

Channel Gmail-Inbox
Master :Gmail-remote:
Slave :Gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel Gmail-sent
Master :Gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :Gmail-local:"Sent Mail"

Channel Gmail-trash
Master :Gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :Gmail-local:Trash

Channel Gmail-drafts
Master :Gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :Gmail-local:Drafts

Channel Gmail-important
Master :Gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Important"
Slave :Gmail-local:Important

Channel Gmail-starred
Master :Gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Starred"
Slave :Gmail-local:Starred

Channel Gmail-cshl
Master :Gmail-remote:CSHL
Slave :Gmail-local:CSHL

Channel Gmail-stony
Master :Gmail-remote:Stony
Slave :Gmail-local:Stony

Group Gmail
Channel Gmail-inbox
Channel Gmail-sent
Channel Gmail-trash
Channel Gmail-drafts
Channel Gmail-important
Channel Gmail-starred
Channel Gmail-cshl
Channel Gmail-stony
